<bibRefCitation id="EFF5C697FF95C4496CAEFD3CF341D7DF" author="Shaw, J. M. H." box="[702,864,738,760]" pageId="10" pageNumber="81" pagination="60 - 78" refId="ref8653" refString="Shaw, J. M. H. (2014) Quarterly supplement to the International register and checklist of orchid hybrids (Sander's list): July - September 2014 registrations. Orchid Review supplement 122: 60 - 78." type="journal article" year="2014">Shaw (2014: 77)</bibRefCitation>
