</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BDBBB66FF95C4496E98FC95F445D6A1" blockId="10.[136,1451,842,905]" pageId="10" pageNumber="81">
We have been unable to obtain samples of 
<taxonomicName id="4C64C0E5FF95C4496C79FC95F34BD64C" authorityName="Chiron" authorityYear="2012" box="[617,874,842,869]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Sansonia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="10" pageNumber="81" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="vandenbergii">
<emphasis id="B9106774FF95C4496C79FC95F34BD64C" box="[617,874,842,869]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="81">Sansonia vandenbergii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to include in our phylogenetic analyses. We follow Chiron (2012) and 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF5C697FF95C4496F4EFCB0F21CD6A1" author="Chiron, G. R. &amp; Karremans, A. P. &amp; van den Berg, C." box="[350,573,878,905]" pageId="10" pageNumber="81" pagination="56 - 62" refId="ref6671" refString="Chiron, G. R., Karremans, A. P. &amp; van den Berg, C. (2016) Nomenclatural notes in the Pleurothallidinae (Orchidaceae): Phloeophila. Phytotaxa 270: 56 - 62. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / phytotaxa. 270.1.6" type="journal article" year="2016">
Chiron 
<emphasis id="B9106774FF95C4496FA3FCB1F1C5D6A0" box="[435,484,878,904]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="81">et al</emphasis>
. (2016)
</bibRefCitation>
who found this species to be related to 
<taxonomicName id="4C64C0E5FF95C4496DE8FCB1F47CD6A0" authorityName="Garay" authorityYear="1974" baseAuthorityName="Schltr." box="[1016,1117,878,905]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Phloeophila" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="10" pageNumber="81" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="bradei">
<emphasis id="B9106774FF95C4496DE8FCB1F47CD6A0" box="[1016,1117,878,905]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="81">S. bradei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
